Class CategoricalCollection

  • java.lang.Object
    • utilities.mapping.CategoricalCollection

  • public class CategoricalCollection
extends java.lang.Object
    This collection stores subsets of categorical values as strings. The structure is a TreeMap whose key is a String and value is a TreeSet that accepts only Strings.
